### Test GrindSettings API Endpoints

### Get all grind settings
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings

### Get all grind settings with filters
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings?minGrindSize=10&maxGrindSize=20&grinderType=Burr

### Get grind setting by ID
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings/1

### Create new grind setting
POST {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grindSize": 15,
  "grindTime": "00:00:30",
  "grindWeight": 20.5,
  "grinderType": "Burr",
  "notes": "Medium grind for pour over"
}

### Update grind setting
PUT {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grindSize": 18,
  "grindTime": "00:00:35",
  "grindWeight": 22.0,
  "grinderType": "Burr",
  "notes": "Updated medium-coarse grind"
}

### Delete grind setting
DELETE {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings/1

### Get recent grind settings
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings/recent?count=5

### Get most used grind settings
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings/most-used?count=5

### Get distinct grinder types
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/grindsettings/grinder-types